These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, eggplant, orange, cucumber
1. the person eating strawberry is on the far left##1
2. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person eating strawberry##3
3. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Food   | strawberry | eggplant | orange | cucumber |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, juice, lemonade
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | almond-milk | lemonade | juice |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, woodworking, skydiving, collecting
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | singing | skydiving | woodworking | collecting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, documentary, fantasy, action
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | family | action | fantasy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, parkour, soccer, cycling
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Sport   | cycling | soccer | parkour | badminton |

