.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-10::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, peas, banana, potato
1. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating potato##1
2. the person eating peas is between the person eating raspberry and the person eating potato##2
3. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
4. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4    |
| Food   | potato | peas | raspberry | banana |

