1. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2    |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | bird | mouse | turtle | cat |

